title: RHONJ: Jackie Non-Joiner
description:
In the wake of Teresa and Jackie's blowout last week, the Real Housewives of New Jersey head to Lake George for some rest, relaxation, and nip slips. What could go wrong?

Watch this recap here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/crappens-on-1434-48019649
